faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實當初都有糾結過係「心中」定「心中」。但喺諗到用「赤子」嘅時候，啱啱同蛋糕中間嘅紅色蠟燭，慢慢融化嘅畫面好似match 咗咁，而上兩句「成熟太熟，還會蠶食」，就好似蠟燭上嘅火咁。<br />\n<br />\n所以就好似特登喺錯同對之間揀咗「中心」。自己覺得喺文法同意思之間有呢啲錯摸位都係有趣，同埋都係學習嘅一部份，所以就試吓喇～<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bee8c6cf2d91b8107fe8d0b1acb0fff3a75a284","tid":2413152,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac78daa2bd8f10bee8e489c37c50dc43af36093","tid":2413152,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:16:01.000Z","msg":"交數未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c55a3ac1914a5da7f3dfb5c5de692cb768ed28","tid":2413152,"uid":392530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T18:55:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/psLY0QiJ1Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpsLY0QiJ1Q4&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=bdee4337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/psLY0QiJ1Q4</a><br />\n&mdash;練詞三 《小飛俠》&mdash; <br />\n開始咗唔夠一個月就已經開始脫更，<br />\n真係道行不夠。<br />\n知道呢個時間冇人睇，但話到明係修行，就算趕通頂都整埋佢啦。<br />\n第一次開口唱，希望大家耳仔屈就屈就。<br />\n<br />\n講返首歌，原曲係由一班高中生年紀嘅日本歌手唱，本來冇好中意，但Youtube係咁Feed畀我，聽聽吓又覺得幾青春，所以又寫吓。<br />\n同好多人一樣，自己小時候過得唔算開心，加上係獨生子，就洐生咗成日自已FF嘅習慣。以前細個都幾負面，成日希望可以脫離呢個世界。但漸漸發覺，可能唔係真係想離開呢個世界，而只係希望有人可以似小飛俠咁，接受內心中幼稚嘅一面，同你面對呢個殘酷嘅世界。懷住呢個心情，寫嘅呢首歌。<br />\n<br />\n原曲：リュックと添い寝ごはん 《生活》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9OVOFU6lPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT9OVOFU6lPQ&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=392ac9ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9OVOFU6lPQ</a> <br />\n<br />\nPlatform<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lin6ci4am1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flin6ci4am1%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1eb6400e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lin6ci4am1/</a><br />\nYT: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3arPcWJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3arPcWJ&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=956b6683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3arPcWJ</a> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lin6ci4am1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flin6ci4am1&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=37338dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lin6ci4am1</a> <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;練詞三 《小飛俠》&mdash; <br />\n<br />\n若 是太急於長大 會吃虧<br />\n沒有卡通可看 他說太浪費<br />\n再做這功課太昂貴<br />\n<br />\n冷衫披肩掛 撘上披風會看見<br />\n怪獸也共你 去玩耍<br />\n小飛俠只可幻想中活着<br />\n都可拉我 離開一趟<br />\n<br />\n來吧 共我飛出這太空<br />\n沒必要 不需介懷沒有鈔票<br />\n如若被鐵勾推出甲板<br />\n彼得潘 都可去為我展開魔法<br />\n<br />\n世道教導我人性太多可怕<br />\n老實努力有時換更多指責<br />\n晚上閉着眼旁聽兩親吵架<br />\n愛太過廉價<br />\n<br />\n確實也沒法分 咒語𥚃偽與真<br />\n這刻只想看見 這個世界大戰沒發生<br />\n小飛俠只可幻想中活着<br />\n都比假希望強<br />\n<br />\n來吧 共我飛出這太空<br />\n沒必要 不需介懷沒放聲笑<br />\n如若被鐵勾推出甲板<br />\n彼得潘 都可去為我展開魔法<br />\n<br />\n來吧 共我飛出這太空<br />\n沒必要 不需介懷沒放聲笑<br />\n如若被鐵勾推出甲板<br />\n彼得潘 都可去為我比劍<br />\n<br />\n來吧 共我飛出這太空<br />\n彼得潘 都可帶着我再一次 渡過"},{"pid":"1f301d164b8ca4eba929c7c10b1d13da5f22b1a1","tid":2413152,"uid":392530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ac78daa2bd8f10bee8e489c37c50dc43af36093","tid":2413152,"uid":385775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:16:01.000Z","msg":"交數未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T18:56:39.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄咁支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次再遲交數打Pat Pat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d45