hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c94a31640a60746acd641a430e92371aa987ced","tid":2413152,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"又一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d520476a8dab8f696f0917a14d14139b958a5b","tid":2413152,"uid":392530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dcdfe15907831c2acdfd143efacddeadf46c7090","tid":2413152,"uid":392530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇試過，聽聽吓啲外語歌，就自動腦補啲詞入去。<br />\n小弟近年就係有呢個情況，於事膽粗粗就寫哂出嚟，同朋友分享。<br />\n點知啲Frd子又話：「幾好喎，不如直頭唱出嚟啦。」<br />\n所以就出現咗呢個習作－<span class=\"x-large\">「練詞庵」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n係練習，又係學習，冇諗過要做啲咩大事，都覺得自己唔夠啲惡搞詞咁幽默，但都希望透過歌詞，分享吓自己成長當中嘅小事。<br />\n如果你鍾意，我會好Happy。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有歌想搵人填，PM我。<br />\n想拎啲詞嚟唱，隨便攞。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">逢星期四晚上9點</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">四個平台同步更新。</span></span><br />\nLIHKG：呢個POST<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lin6ci4am1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flin6ci4am1%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1eb6400e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lin6ci4am1/</a><br />\nYT: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3u5gPg9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3u5gPg9&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=00f50868\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3u5gPg9</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lin6ci4am1/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flin6ci4am1%2F%20&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=cdddbf4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lin6ci4am1/ </a><br />\n<br />\n暫時目標係堅持到一年。<br />\n希望大家多屌，多支持<br />\n<br />\n繼續向下碌，即刻有歌聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VJXi3E9Jx_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVJXi3E9Jx_A&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=92454f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VJXi3E9Jx_A</a> <br />\n－練詞四 《空手道》－<br />\n<br />\n呢首係其中一首我稱呼為「加油歌」嘅作品，內容好直都唔使多講。<br />\n所以怕怕醜醜咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一開始寫詞係想幫自己打打氣，好似一個自己鼓勵自己嘅過程咁。<br />\n所以就算有時覺得老生常談，甚至有啲老土都好，都好知醜咁寫哂出嚟。講創意，當然唔夠其他人啦。<br />\n不過我又覺得，有時最鼓舞到我哋嘅嘢，真係唔使太「啜核」。一碗青紅蘿蔔湯，一碟豆腐火腩飯，可能比魚翅花膠Omakase更溫暖到我哋。<br />\n<br />\n今個星期又係小弟唱住先，又要大家耳仔屈就屈就。下星期有返朋友仔代歌，希望大家繼續多多支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n原曲：osage《ウーロンハイと春に》<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnpA41qNgpY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrnpA41qNgpY&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=3f834cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnpA41qNgpY</a> <br />\n<br />\nPlatform<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lin6ci4am1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flin6ci4am1%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1eb6400e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lin6ci4am1/</a><br />\nYT: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3arPcWJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3arPcWJ&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=956b6683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3arPcWJ</a> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lin6ci4am1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flin6ci4am1&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=37338dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lin6ci4am1</a> <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n－練詞四 《空手道》－<br />\n<br />\n明明在走 為何眼內全是倒退<br />\n明明沒走 為何感覺像去追<br />\n明明沒好勝 仍總不禁去做比較 <br />\n難道與現實賽跑 提速有用嗎<br />\n<br />\n其實是否 無前進也無謂退卻<br />\n人類是否 動力只靠着逐流<br />\n童夢被冷落 成人只管有價值功課 <br />\n還未開竅 成長經已略過 ￼       <br />\n<br />\n全是過程 無論結果<br />\n兜兜轉轉再抱着再多 終需流逝的一切<br />\n如若沒有 還是放開手<br />\n需知道終點方向不用回首<br />\n誰都空手去走<br />\n<br />\n常常目睹 誰人眼淚流在腦𥚃<br />\n曾在幻想 能為他去受傷 <br />\n其實未試過 便沾沾讚嘆曾想過<br />\n亦曾為歡笑 自私欺騙別個<br />\n<br />\n如果一出生便能成大器<br />\n才發覺這心理 這個想法 確實小家子氣<br />\n當你不再假設一切 從來無完美<br />\n完美設計出你 所有經過將你修理<br />\n<br />\n當迷失於分叉路 想着退縮<br />\n便來暫時換口氣 無常會 如常引導你我 <br />\n<br />\n全是過程 從沒結果<br />\n兜兜轉轉再放下更多 都不會目空一切<br />\n其實沒有 來吧放開手<br />\n需知道終點方向不用回首<br />\n誰都空手去走<br />\n<br />\n不再虛構<br />\n來或去都放手"},{"pid":"89579eb7e440157e6a0c1246ca7a2509d3dcf932","tid":2413152,"uid":392530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c94a31640a60746acd641a430e92371aa987ced","tid":2413152,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"又一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"差啲又出唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝巴打科勞啊，記住下星期又返嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028bbeeb2dde66213eb0e3bfbc94cc35703da72d","tid":2413152,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"今晚好準時喎"},{"pid":"b1299527e532594c514fcd9fd9aff241152de517","tid":2413152,"uid":87765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"靚聲靚詞、強帖留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a90b33d11e2d17afbaf01f02ef9eec057c38380","tid":2413152,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse